C
   y\frac{dy}{dx}+\frac{3}{2x}y^2==\frac{d}{dx}\frac{y^2}{2}+\frac{3}{x}\frac{y^2}{2}=-2. 
    \frac{dz}{dx}+\frac{3}{x}z=-2 
    z=z_0(x)+kx 
    \frac{y^2}{2}=\frac{C}{x^3}-\frac{1}{2}x. 
